OL,3,CWave of bus strikes threatened over
OL,4,Cpay and conditions
OL,6,FFurther strikes involving thousands
OL,7,Fmore bus workers are planned at other
OL,8,Ftowns and cities in the coming weeks.
OL,10,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,11,Fsaid: "Bus employers everywhere need
OL,12,Fto get the message loud and clear:
OL,13,Fdriver pay simply does not reflect the
OL,14,Fstresses and strains of the job.
OL,16,F"Fatigue, a lack of toilets, abuse and
OL,17,Feven assaults are a daily occurrence.
OL,19,F"Unite will fight tooth and nail for
OL,20,Fbus workers until wages and conditions
OL,21,Fimprove across the sector."
