OL,3,CWave of bus strikes threatened over
OL,4,Cpay and conditions
OL,6,FUnite has previously reported that bus
OL,7,Fdrivers face abuse at work, with
OL,8,Fworkers reporting that the number of
OL,9,Fincidents is increasing.
OL,11,FThe union is also campaigning for
OL,12,Fimprovements to rest breaks, toilet
OL,13,Ffacilities and shift patterns to
OL,14,Freduce fatigue.
OL,16,FBus drivers are more likely to suffer
OL,17,Fmental and physical ill health than
OL,18,Fother professions due to the stressful
OL,19,Fnature of the job, according to the
OL,20,Funion.
